{"tid":664512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"力壓普京  習近平獲Forbes選為2018權勢人物首位  在中國 \"被消失\"","createTime":"2018-05-14T06:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T07:45:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b711178557d6bfc0c4ae4931af9c96e8761b88","tid":664512,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:43:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%8D%B2forbes%E9%81%B8%E7%82%BA2018%E6%AC%8A%E5%8B%A2%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E9%A6%96%E4%BD%8D-%E9%99%B8%E5%AA%92%E5%99%A4%E8%81%B2-051726803.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%258D%25B2forbes%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%2582%25BA2018%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%258B%25A2%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25AA%2592%25E5%2599%25A4%25E8%2581%25B2-051726803.html&d=H1LxElxrqP%2BjdOOa2Pcn9fiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=dad70d0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%8D%B2forbes%E9%81%B8%E7%82%BA2018%E6%AC%8A%E5%8B%A2%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E9%A6%96%E4%BD%8D-%E9%99%B8%E5%AA%92%E5%99%A4%E8%81%B2-051726803.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國「富比世」雜誌，選出今年的「全球最有權勢人物榜」，中國國家主席習近平，第一次登上榜首。不過大陸媒體在報導之後不久，卻紛紛把報導刪除，原因不明。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n富比世雜誌是在五月八號，公布二○一八年的「全球最有權勢人物」排行榜，習近平擠下四連霸的俄羅斯總統普丁，第一次進入全球權勢榜榜首。有國外媒體發現，大陸媒體報導之後，又全部刪除。如果用百度搜尋引擎搜尋，只能看到二○一七年之前的排行榜，今年的則是完全沒有畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而富比世解釋習近平進入全球權勢榜第一名的原因，是由於今年三月，中國全國人大修憲，擴大習近平的權力，並取消國家主席任期限制，使他享有中國大陸自毛澤東以來，僅見的個人崇拜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而據美國之音報導，刪除這則報導的舉動，「顯然不是這些媒體的自我檢肅，而必定是來自於中共高層」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b292f13c5e88270264e8d0658ad5ee75e557b5","tid":664512,"uid":77959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:57:19.000Z","msg":"心諗乜嘢富比世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你原來係福布斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c26d793acaca281284266a586559d69587c54d","tid":664512,"uid":41204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:31:45.000Z","msg":"岩架啦 繼續分化習近平同普京 想佢地狗咬狗骨"},{"pid":"58f01421b55897b0ddb532f03cef03a7ff12e2b5","tid":664512,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942c12be5e4ce01182580bb5ed699d94fa2f0cd8","tid":664512,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:39:51.000Z","msg":"刁總真係好humble"},{"pid":"88f5083cbef27ac3d3f220632b66fc4c0740acdd","tid":664512,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"美國佬捧殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5b4dc2c5a5af34ca7ca5f716c180afaa613d39","tid":664512,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69c26d793acaca281284266a586559d69587c54d","tid":664512,"uid":41204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:31:45.000Z","msg":"岩架啦 繼續分化習近平同普京 想佢地狗咬狗骨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:42:00.000Z","msg":"鄰國人點夠戰鬥民族打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539143b54221db6c14072b56c3305adaca6d8e42","tid":664512,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"崩口人忌......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9408b83ed72ffd1bf662ce9a5e84314647c1f7","tid":664512,"uid":133529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"吸精平，冇料扮四條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/d